
DESCRIPTION
-----------

Library designed for deal with arbitrary-precision arithmetic. Also, a simple
example is provided.


COMPILING
---------

Compile it entering the command "make". You will need the GCC compiler and the
GNU Make tool.


RUNNING THE TEST PROGRAM
------------------------

	Usage: bignumber

The program will test the falseness of the affirmation

1841^12 + 1782^12 = 1922^12

The former equality appeared in the Simpsons episode "Treehouse of Horror VI"
(http://www.snpp.com/episodes/3F04.html)